reviews.productTitle: GE Rocker Dimmer Switch Rocker On/Off Light Switch Dimmer Switches for LED Lights Single Pole Energy Saving UL Listed White 10464
reviews.text: I ordered and installed a number of these back in September 2022. Within a year one started making the light flicker at in-between power levels. Now I have had four of them break making it impossible to turn them on or off. The white post in the cover eventually breaks under normal use. These switches are not durable. I bought another brand to replace them, switches that simply have a slider for on/off and dimming whickhwould seem to be more durable by design.

reviews.title: They Didn’t Last

reviews.productTitle: GE Rocker Dimmer Switch Rocker On/Off Light Switch Dimmer Switches for LED Lights Single Pole Energy Saving UL Listed White 10464
reviews.text: I purchased two of these GE rocker style dimmer. It was the switch I I selected as it had dimmer feature and manufactured by famous GE, and was reasonably priced. The order was back ordered by several weeks so I called off my licensed electrician until they arrived on August 13, 2024. Electrician was a month out and came to install them on September 16, 2024. Unfortunately, one worked as it should and one was defected. The electrician performed a simple test on the defective switch, which confirmed it was inoperable. I wish I knew there was a test I could have performed within the 30 return period, now the cost for the good switch just doubled. It is said that if you have one foot in a pail of hot water and one foot in a pail of cold water, statically you are comfortable - but a 50% "reject" on this famous brand of switch has earned it 2 1/2 star rating, not very comfortable.
reviews.date: Reviewed in the United States on September 27, 2024
reviews.title: HAVE SWITCHED CHECKED BY ELECTRICIAN IF INSTALLATION DELAYED BEYOND ALLOWED RETURN
